<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Leng-leng leng aw thangvan sang ah,
 Mei leh ngomei haw khel in;
 Va leng leng kumsawt sau lunnuom
 Salem thak khawpi chullo,
 A In huong cham sana tuia,
 Kiluon achun tuolkum in,
 Khuo thil ingka gam hing mun nuom,
 A hehpihna vak nuoi ah.

[V2]
 Ka ngai ngei kumsawt saulun nuom,
 Angel leh zuomang umna,
 Aw pak tin thanghaw a pak lun,
 Hinna tui a luong heu heu,

[V3]
 2. Zie gam hawih a va lengte chun,
 Khawvel hi nungtieng sawn in
 Zuomang chung Pathien sau lunah
 Luon thi nulna um talo
 Teutui thien bangin a thieng ui,
 A sakmel uh tuoi ngeilo
 Chung sun nisa a thuok ta puou
 Ninnuom laituol a leng ui.

[V4]
 3. Dan leh lenguol lungdeihte tawh,
 Zuo saulun ah zaila sa'n,
 I ngaih Zuomang kawma um in,
 Nunnuom in zaila sai tiu,
 Ka gelin a ngaiin ka kap;
 Lungdeih cheng laituol lenna
 Lautha cheng kim hun ding ngak ui,
 Aw hin Thing nah lim nuoi ah.</lyrics>
<title>Hinna Tui Luonna</title>
<author>Kamlala</author>
<hymn_number>229</hymn_number>
</song>